      <text>Environmental dissemination of mcr-1 positive Enterobacteriaceae by Chrysomya spp. (common blowfly): An increasing public health risk.</text>
      <annotation id="1">
        <infon key="identifier"></infon>
        <infon key="type">Gene</infon>
